title: Limited Time -Low Pricing!
posting_body: ['The Highlands of Marin offers remarkable amenities, premier resident services and eco-friendly apartments in San Rafael.', 'From sweeping views of San Rafael to chic amenities at every turn, Highlands of Marin offers upscale apartment living near the best of Marin County and downtown San Francisco.', 'Enjoy generous community amenities like two swimming pools, a dog park, and 24-hour fitness center.', 'Experience a sunset from your private patio or curl up by the wood-burning fireplace in your apartment at the Highlands.', 'Take full advantage of a country getaway with all the conveniences of city living.', 'Visit our website: <URL> to view our availability and pricing, take a 3D Tour of this apartment or schedule your preference of a virtually guided or self-guided tour.', "We can't wait to show you what Highlands of Marin has in store as your new home!", 'From sweeping views of San Rafael to chic amenities at every turn, Highlands of Marin offers upscale apartment living near the best of Marin County and downtown San Francisco.', 'Enjoy generous community amenities like two swimming pools, a dog park, and 24-hour fitness center.', 'Experience a sunset from your private patio or curl up by the wood-burning fireplace in your apartment at the Highlands.', 'Take full advantage of a country getaway with all the conveniences of city living.', ' Explore available apartments at Highlands of Marin - now complete with the Smart Home package!', 'VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'Highlands of Marin, managed by UDR', '1001 Cresta Way', 'San Rafael, CA 94903', 'show contact info', 'Monday By Appointment Only', 'Tuesday', 'By Appointment', 'Only', 'Wednesday By Appointment Only', 'Thursday By Appointment Only', 'Friday By Appointment', 'Only', 'Saturday By Appointment Only']
